{"content":[{"id":"717677a2","settings":{"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"7f1b8795","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"align":"center","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"114ba0d9","settings":{"image":{"url":"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/The-Women-in-Engineering-Image.jpg","id":64512,"size":"","alt":"","source":"library"},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"image","elType":"widget"},{"id":"48809939","settings":{"editor":"<p>Diversity in the field of civil engineering is more important than ever and at the Engineering Management Institute (EMI), we are focused on using our platform to facilitate diversity and inclusion in engineering.\u00a0 Therefore, we have launched a series entitled Women in Civil Engineering (#WomeninCE) on The Civil Engineering Podcast and we will post all series episodes on this page.<\/p>\n<p>Scroll down to view them or nominate someone,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/civil-engineering-podcast\/id993416182?ls=1&amp;mt=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">click here to subscribe to the podcast<\/a>, and most importantly, please share across social media if you would like to help bring attention to the great things women are doing in civil engineering.\u00a0 You can simply share this image below.\u00a0 Thank you!<\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"6fed16e1","settings":{"image":{"url":"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\